 er litt utenfor \u00e5 holde sammen med\u00bb, ble det sagt p\u00e5 foreldresamtalen. Jeg gikk bort fra \u00e5 v\u00e6re usynlig, til \u00e5 bli vanskelig. Kverulerende, trassig. En elev som ikke hilser p\u00e5 l\u00e6rerne i gangen. Ser ned, holder pusten. Hvorfor hilse, ordene kommer likevel ikke ut? Angsten har spist dem.", "Kj\u00e6re l\u00e6rer, jeg skulle \u00f8nske at du s\u00e5 meg den gangen, som den eleven som hadde det s\u00e5 fryktelig vondt.", "Anna"]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "incoming"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "2e7fabd716c16cb39a4389dcf83896545ade37867878cde389ca54842bfc4fa6"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2015-09-01T05:31:54.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Sp\u00f8r du hvordan hun har det f\u00f8r du gir opp?"}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article11489712.ece/hj7p7z/ALTERNATES/w980-default/wsdgtrewgt%20(2).jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/a2ed0aef66b51d6ff52d62e066348929c1baa993.jpg?5948d17b"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": "Kj\u00e6re du som er l\u00e6rer -adressa.no"}, {"field": "id", "value": "a2ed0aef66b51d6ff52d62e066348929c1baa993"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": "Snakk ut"}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "Snakk ut"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": "incoming"}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "education"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["l\u00e6rer", "syne", "barna", "skole", "elev"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": "incoming"}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article11489712.ece/hj7p7z/ALTERNATES/w980-default/wsdgtrewgt%20(2).jpg"}, {"field": "og-locale", "value": "nb_NO"}, {"field": "og-site-name", "value": "adressa.no"}, {"field": "og-title", "value": "Kj\u00e6re du som er l\u0